p: The STRING database and the Cytoscape software were used to construct the PPI network of the overlapping DEGs in EOC. Finally, three important clusters were screened by MCODE. Among them, cluster 1 included 59 proteins with the highest score (Fig. 3a), cluster 2 and 3 contained 15 and 5 proteins, respectively (Fig. 3b & c). Additionally, we analyzed the function of cluster 1. In KEGG analysis, the cluster 1′ DEGs were mostly enriched in Cell cycle and Oocyte meiosis (Fig. 3d). In GO analysis, cluster 1′ DEGs were mostly enriched in Protein binding, Nucleoplasm and Nucleus (Fig. 3e).
